<abstract>
<para>
&neuroscope; is a viewer for displaying various physiological and behavioral data. It allows comparison of analyzed data with the original recordings.
</para>
<para>
&neuroscope; is developped by Lynn Hazan in <ulink url="http://osiris.rutgers.edu">G. Buzsáki's lab</ulink> (CMBN, Rutgers Newark, USA).
</para>
</abstract>

