</varlistentry>
<varlistentry>
<term><menuchoice>
<guimenu>Units</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Waveforms</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice></term>
<listitem><para>Draws spike waveforms for selected clusters directly on the local field potential traces.</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>
